summary: Louis Tomlinson - Two of Us (Official Video)  Good Morning!  Morning Update for Two of Us.  The video is now at 2,011,987 at...
caption:
Louis Tomlinson - Two of Us (Official Video)

Good Morning!  Morning Update for Two of Us.  The video is now at 2,011,987 at 8:00 am EST.  This is amazing.  I will be trying to keep track of where we stand in streaming numbers for the Brit Awards or any other award ceremony!!!  

Stream when you have a few moments.  Use your mobile, pc, or tablet! It all adds up.  If only 100,000 people watched it 10 times that’s 1 million views a day (which adds up to approximately 36 minutes), which at that rate we would have 100 million by approximately August 18th.  It’s a Goal !!!  While watching/streaming you could kill two birds with one stone.  The Billboards Social 50 uses YouTube interaction as part of their system so

While you are watching or streaming:

1. watch all ads

2. REFRESH. Do not replay.

3. Periodically use the search bar to look for the video.

4. Use incognito and refresh extension to play multiple times while you are away doing other things.

5. Comment often

6. use other accounts to like and comment

7. Share to your facebook timeline or other timelines. I created an alternative Facebook and a managed account to share to via all my YouTube/Email accounts

8. Share to pintrest or instagram

9. Tweet it from your fan account

10. Use the Shazam app while watching.  It will add to radio play.

Thanks for all you do for Louis and the boys!!

Please reblog!!!
